IPS Laboratory tests and panels

Intensional Value Set Definition: LOINC {  {    STATUS in {ACTIVE}    CLASSTYPE in {1}    CLASS exclude {CHALSKIN, H&P.HX.LAB, H&P.HX, NR STATS, PATH.PROTOCOLS.*}  } } 

This value set includes codes from the following code systems:

  • Include codes from http://loinc.org where STATUS = ACTIVE and http://loinc.org where CLASSTYPE = 1 and http://loinc.org where CLASS matches (by regex) ^(?!PATH\.PROTOCOLS.*$).* and http://loinc.org where CLASS matches (by regex) ^(?!NR STATS.*$).* and http://loinc.org where CLASS matches (by regex) ^(?!H&P\.HX.*$).* and http://loinc.org where CLASS matches (by regex) ^(?!H&P\.HX\.LAB.*$).* and http://loinc.org where CLASS matches (by regex) ^(?!CHALSKIN.*$).*
